      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this car in person. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, and it\u2019s spotless inside and out\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like an absolute dream, too. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the 'new car' price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
